# Smart Salary Predictor

A machine learning web app that predicts salary based on job profile details and gives career suggestions.

## Tech Stack

Python, Pandas, Scikit-learn, Flask, Streamlit, Plotly, Joblib

## Features

- Salary prediction using Ridge Regression
- Interactive Streamlit frontend
- Flask API backend
- Career suggestions based on user inputs
- Salary visualization using Plotly

## How to Run

First run the Flask backend:

```bash
python app.py

